预先警告：“实验性1级”功能！该功能于0.4加入 Warning: experimental function (1st level) introduced in 0.4 从本版本开始，设计者引入了“实验功能评级”系统，以区分各个实验功能。而本应用中的“实验性1级”的功能是指有设想但是具体实现不健全（包括代码不稳定和具体实现仍有问题）的功能。使用它们可能导致系统错乱，请三思再使用！ From now on, the designer introduced "experimental function rate" system to tell apart different experimental function. The 1st grade means that the function is imagined but the way to make it may be not good (including buggy code and some problems). Using them may cause system error, please think twice before using it!
双语模式已启动实验性3级 Bilingual mode is on experimental function (3rd level) 现在系统可以同时显示2个语言，或许对你有帮助呢！ Now two languages can be shown at the same time, which might be helpful for you!
为什么这是实验性3级应用？ Why is this a 3rd grade experimental function?
